This paper belongs to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category as it focuses on designing an interface that is more user-friendly and engaging for a broader range of citizens. The use of natural language interactions also suggests a connection to Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the chatbot's ability to suggest relevant open datasets implies the use of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the potential for viral dissemination through social media platforms like Facebook and Skype suggests a connection to the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-category.
